{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]I saw my castles fall [G7]today
[C]And crumble into dust around my feet
[G7]In shambles there my future lay
[D7]Each stone a broken dream so [G7]sweet
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[C]I built a heaven in the [F]sky
[D7]Where my true love and I could [G7]stay
