[C]I saw my castles fall today
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[G7]I say my castles fall today
[C]My world came tumbling down before my eyes
[G7]I know it's faded I must pay
[D7]For building castles in the [G7]sky
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
[C]Amid the ruins of all my [F]schemes
